{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "“起始之人” 第23章 2-1 傀儡与大门",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "法尔艾斯和贝维特满意地\\n眺望着圣都格拉姆斯的混乱景象。\\n原来他们的目的是收集瘴气打开\\n通向封印“起始之人”异界的大门。\\n“起始之人”的复活之时将近。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯？",
            "context": "终于走到这一步了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯？",
            "context": "被那家伙封印以来……\\n究竟经过了多少岁月。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯？",
            "context": "终于可以创造\\n让吾回归的大门了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "嗯？法尔艾斯哥哥？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯？",
            "context": "怎么了，贝维特？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "感觉你怪怪的……\\n就像换了个人似的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯？",
            "context": "换了个人？啊，也是。\\n回归的准备逐渐就绪，\\n所以这副身体也受到了影响吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯？",
            "context": "无需担心，贝维特。\\n这正说明距离目标的达成\\n已经越来越近。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "是吗……那就好……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯？",
            "context": "这副身体不过是\\n“起始之人”的傀儡。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯？",
            "context": "由于吾的意志还没能彻底降临，\\n所以目前还是在以法尔艾斯的\\n自我认知来行动……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯？",
            "context": "回归之日越近，就会越接近\\n“起始之人”的意志了吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯？",
            "context": "但是这并不会造成什么改变，\\n你只要按照吾的意志行动便是。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "……\\n嗯……好的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "那我应该……做什么呢？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯？",
            "context": "你去收集遍布这圣都的瘴气。\\n你有为此所需的力量。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯？",
            "context": "吾从1000年前开始就一直在\\n引导瘴气聚集到这片大地之上。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯？",
            "context": "比如魔神，那家伙真是好用，\\n很有效率地唤来了\\n“起始之人”的力量。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯？",
            "context": "对了，\\n伊莉雅教用起来也十分顺手。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯？",
            "context": "多亏了他们，1000年来这圣都的\\n大地之上，憎恶、执迷、妒忌、鄙夷……\\n种种恶意不曾断绝。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯？",
            "context": "这一切化作如今笼罩这里的瘴气。\\n收集这些瘴气，\\n就能打开让吾回归的大门。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "你说收集，是要收集到哪里？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯？",
            "context": "呵呵……这里，这副身体中。\\n这副身体正是成就\\n吾之回归的容器。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "把瘴气集中到法尔艾斯哥哥的体内！？\\n这么做的话，法尔艾斯哥哥不就……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯？",
            "context": "自然会失去容器本身。\\n但这并不是什么问题。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "怎、怎么能这样说……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯？",
            "context": "正如吾刚才所言，\\n这副身体不过是“起始之人”的傀儡。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯？",
            "context": "而且，作为傀儡应该\\n也已经接近极限了。\\n这副身体正在逐渐腐朽。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯？",
            "context": "毕竟长时间承受着\\n“起始之人”的意志和力量，\\n也难免会坏掉。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯？",
            "context": "不过作为傀儡，\\n这已经算是坚持得够久的了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "傀儡……\\n你说的傀儡是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯？",
            "context": "就是遵从“起始之人”的意志，\\n并以此为目的而行动的人偶啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯？",
            "context": "被关在异界的“起始之人”\\n无法直接干预别的世界。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯？",
            "context": "为此，吾会将那个世界的人类\\n变为吾的人偶，\\n让其为吾之回归而行动。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯？",
            "context": "这可是相当令吾头疼的功能。\\n一般的人类单是承受\\n吾的意志便会坏掉。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯？",
            "context": "能找到这个叫法尔艾斯的人类，\\n对“起始之人”而言实属幸运。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯？",
            "context": "能让“起始之人”的意志\\n降临到如此程度的傀儡，\\n这还是头一个。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯？",
            "context": "毕竟甚至还有傀儡\\n连自己受到吾的意志操控\\n都觉察不到呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯？",
            "context": "正因如此，这个法尔艾斯才是\\n迎接吾之回归最合适的那扇门。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯？",
            "context": "去吧，贝维特。\\n去收集这片大地上\\n积攒了1000年的瘴气吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯？",
            "context": "如今正是以我之躯……\\n迎吾回归之时！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "希望你不要为这种无聊的事\\n去利用我宝贵的兄弟们呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯？",
            "context": "唔？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01",
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "我不会让你得逞的，“起始之人”。\\n无论是兄长的肉体，还是贝维特，\\n我都要从你手中夺回。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_23_02_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}